data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and versatility in this inviting two bedroom home featuring three non-conforming bedrooms in the basement, ideal for office space, guests or hobbies, with two bathrooms and an attached garage, convenience meets functionality. Step outside to your serene fenced backyard oasis, perfect for outdoor gatherings or quiet relaxation. This charming residence offers ample living spaces and endless possibilities in a desirable neighborhood. **Newer roof**Don't miss out the opportunity to call this gem yours.
